  "conclusion": {
    "zh": "【SCFI vs 台灣周邊商船流量分析（n=6 週）】\n• 商船（貨+油）與 SCFI 綜合指數呈 中度負相關 (Pearson r=-0.417, p=0.4110, 未達統計顯著)\n• 最佳滯後: lag=2 週，r=-0.605 → 船舶流量領先 SCFI 2 週\n• 預測可行性: ⚠️ 存在 中度負相關，但未通過 Granger 因果檢驗，不建議單獨用於預測\n• 註：SCFI 為週資料，小樣本下結論僅供參考；建議持續累積至 30 週以上再作決策依據。",
    "en": "[SCFI vs Taiwan-area Commercial Vessels (n=6 weeks)] Commercial vessels (cargo+tanker) vs SCFI composite: Pearson r=-0.417, p=0.4110. Best lag: 2 weeks (r=-0.605) - vessel traffic leads SCFI by 2 weeks. moderate negative correlation detected but no Granger causality; not recommended for standalone prediction.",
